| Present mode (Standard, Presenter View, Record, Autoplay) | All four modes free |
| Export as JPG or PNG | Standard quality (96 DPI), no watermark |
| Batch PNG export (all pages) | Share → Download → PNG → All pages → separate numbered files |
| MP4 video export (up to 1080p, up to 30 min) | Respects design orientation — vertical design = vertical MP4 |
| Text effects (Shadow, Lift, Hollow, Splice, Outline, Echo, Glitch, Neon, Curve, Background) | All 10+ built-in text effects free |
| Drop shadow on images | Follows actual person shape, not rectangle — **verified** |
| Outline/stroke on images | Follows actual person shape, not rectangle — **verified** |
| Photo filters (presets) | Solar, Festive, Retro, Cali, Summer, Drama, Nordic, Epic, and more |
