| Elements library (partial) | 3+ million free graphics, arrows, icons — filter by "Free" to avoid Pro elements |
| Face Retouch | Smoothes skin, brightens eyes |
| Liquify | Bloat, Pinch, Swirl distortion brushes |
| Auto Focus | Subject detection + background blur |
| Color Edit | Customizes highlights/shadows to match colors |
