| 5GB cloud storage | Per free account |
| 1 Brand Kit (3 colors, 2 fonts only) | Basic branding — no custom font uploads |
| Up to 200 Standard AI uses or 20 Premium AI uses/month | Resets monthly |
| Twitch overlay, panel, and banner templates | Free templates at 1920×1080px |

### ❌ Pro Only (Requires Paid Plan)

| Feature | Why It Matters | Workaround |
|---|---|---|
| Background Remover (photo) | One-click AI cutout | Use **remove.bg** instead — better results anyway |
| Background Remover (video) | No free trial at all | No good free alternative |
| Magic Eraser | Paint over objects to remove them | Photopea (free, browser-based) |
| Magic Edit | AI generative fill/replace | No direct free equivalent |
| Transparent background export | PNG with transparency | Use remove.bg + chroma key in OBS (green background workaround) |
| Magic Resize / Magic Switch | One-click resize design to new dimensions | Create new canvas at target size, manually copy-paste elements |
| Custom font uploads | Upload TTF/OTF files | Use Canva's 3,000+ built-in fonts — most Google Fonts available natively |
| Export quality/size slider | Scale output 0.5×–3.125× original | Standard 96 DPI export sufficient for OBS and screen display |
| Full Brand Kit | Unlimited color palettes, logo storage, font uploads, saved templates | Brand board workaround (see below) |
| 100GB+ cloud storage | — | 5GB free sufficient for current workflow |
| Match and Move (transitions) | Morphing slide transitions | Not relevant |
| Video Background Remover | Remove background from video clips | No good free alternative |
| Magic Morph (text) | AI-stylized text from prompt | Not relevant |
| 4K MP4 export | Up to 3840×2160 | 1080p free export sufficient |
| Magic Shortcuts (presentations) | C for confetti, B for blur, D for drumroll | Not relevant |

### ⚠️ Partially Free (Important Nuance)

**Image outline on people:** The Outline effect in Shadows panel is free and follows the person shape. However, it only works correctly on images with a transparent background. Since Canva's Background Remover is Pro, you need to remove the background with remove.bg first, then upload to Canva. The outline effect itself is free — the workflow just requires the external tool.

**Elements library:** Millions of elements are free. Premium elements show a crown icon. Always filter by "Free" when searching Elements to avoid accidentally placing Pro assets that will export with a watermark.

**Brand Kit:** Free accounts get 1 Brand Kit with 3 colors and 2 fonts from Canva's built-in library only. No custom font uploads, no logo storage, no saved brand templates.

**Present mode:** All four modes are free. Vertical designs display centered on landscape monitors with black bars (pillarboxing) on left and right sides — this is expected behavior, not a bug.

**AI allowance:** Free accounts get up to 200 Standard AI uses or 20 Premium AI uses per month. Resets monthly.

