## Pricing Reference (April 2026)

| Plan | Price | Key additions over Free |
|---|---|---|
| Free | €0 | Everything listed in the Free section above |
| Pro | ~€110/year (~€15/month) | Background Remover, Magic Resize, Magic Eraser, Magic Edit, transparent export, custom fonts, 100GB storage, 5 Brand Kits, 4K export |
| Business | ~€170/year per person | 100 Brand Kits, 500GB storage, team admin tools, 20x AI allowance |

**Is Pro worth it for EIW right now?** No. The remove.bg workaround handles the one meaningful thumbnail gap. Magic Resize is the most relevant Pro feature — it would save time when repurposing lecture slides to vertical format — but it's not urgent while the editing workflow is still being hired out. Revisit when repurposing content across formats becomes a regular task. A **30-day free trial** is available — worth using strategically to batch-resize existing designs and set up a full Brand Kit.

