## Font Reference

### Recommended for EIW mythology aesthetic (all free in Canva)
- **Cinzel / Cinzel Decorative** — myth titles, hero text. Roman/classical feel. Correct for mythology.
- **Cormorant Garamond** — secondary text, descriptions. Elegant, readable at small sizes.
- **Playfair Display** — alternative heading font. Literary, sophisticated.
- **Alegreya / Alegreya Sans** — readable body text with a literary quality.

### Other available free fonts (general use)
- Montserrat, Oswald, Bebas Neue, Anton, Raleway, Lora, Merriweather, Bangers

### Uploading Custom Fonts
- Requires **Pro** — uses Brand Kit font upload
- Free workaround: most Google Fonts are available natively in Canva without uploading
- Check Canva's font search before assuming a font is unavailable

